"<span style="font-size: 22px; font-weight: 400; line-height: normal">Submission MCR-MN-0004-SNBC is no longer subject to review</span><br />
  This determination is based on your updated submission responses.<br />
  <br />
<b>Submitted by:</b> <a href="mailto:house@example.com">house@example.com</a><br /> 
<b>Updated on:</b> 03/08/2026<br />
<b>New review decision:</b> Not subject to formal review and approval<br />
<br />
<b>Summary of changes:</b> Updated info<br /><br />
<a href="http://localhost/submissions/eqro/test-contract-123">View submission</a><br />
<br />
  <b>As a reminder, all contracts with EQROs must:</b>
<ul style="margin-top: 0;">
    <li>
        Be submitted to CMS. This includes base contracts, amendments to base contracts, and extensions.
    </li>
    <li>
        Meet competence and independence requirements specified at 42 CFR 438.354 to qualify for Federal Financial Participation (FFP).
    </li>
    <li>
        Require the mandatory review activities specified at 42 CFR 438.358 for MCOs, PIHPs, and PAHPs.
    </li>
</ul>If you need to make further changes, contact <a href="mailto:MCGDMCOactions@cms.hhs.gov">MCGDMCOactions@cms.hhs.gov</a>."
`;

